ern-spa-interior-design-190625-851-08-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-interior-design-190625-851-08-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-interior-design-190625-851-08-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-interior-design-190625-851-09.jpg\" alt=\"Step into a sensory cocoon on the first floor of SIAM SPA, where flowing corridors, sand-toned textures, and curved walls evoke the feeling of a peaceful, natural cave. Intimate lighting and tactile materials create a tranquil setting for massage and deep relaxation.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-interior-design-190625-851-09.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-interior-design-190625-851-09-940x1253.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-interior-design-190625-851-09-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-interior-design-190625-851-09-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-interior-design-190625-851-09-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-interior-design-190625-851-09-1536x2048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003eFitness in Focus\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eUpstairs, the mood shifts. The entire second floor is dedicated to fitness and carries a more restrained aesthetic. Smooth grey plastered surfaces are paired with veined wood textures, creating a refined backdrop for movement and discipline. Tall, living plants echo the organic feel of the spa below, offering a sense of continuity across floors.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eCustom-designed fitness equipment, made of wood to match the space, is tailored for stretching, manual training, and flexibility. Every detail here reinforces the overall vision: to merge functionality with calm, natural beauty.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1439\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/gym-check-in-area-190625-843-01.jpg\" alt=\" The second floor of SIAM SPA takes on a more minimalist mood with smooth grey walls, veined wood accents, and lush greenery. Custom wooden fitness equipment blends beauty with function, offering a serene environment for stretching, strength, and movement.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/gym-check-in-area-190625-843-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/gym-check-in-area-190625-843-01-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/gym-check-in-area-190625-843-01-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/gym-check-in-area-190625-843-01-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/gym-check-in-area-190625-843-01-1536x1151.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1439\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/gym-check-in-area-190625-843-012.jpg\" alt=\"The second floor of SIAM SPA takes on a more minimalist mood with smooth grey walls, veined wood accents, and lush greenery. Custom wooden fitness equipment blends beauty with function, offering a serene environment for stretching, strength, and movement.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/gym-check-in-area-190625-843-012.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/w