vw, 1919px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003eStreamlined Cosmetology\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe top floor houses the cosmetology unit, designed with a more minimal material palette but staying within the warm, earthy tones of the spa. This choice reflects the space’s need for sterility and adaptability, while still aligning with the holistic, nature-rooted ethos of the project.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1439\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-lobby-190625-851-01.jpg\" alt=\"The cosmetology level of this contemporary spa features clean lines and soft natural tones for a calming, clinical feel. Designed for mobility and sterility, this floor maintains the spa’s earthy palette while supporting advanced facial and skincare treatments.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-lobby-190625-851-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-lobby-190625-851-01-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-lobby-190625-851-01-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-lobby-190625-851-01-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-lobby-190625-851-01-1536x1151.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1919\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/modern-spa-lobby-190625-851-02.jpg\" alt=\"The cosmetology level of this contemporary spa features clean lines and soft natural tones for a calming, clinical feel. Designed for mobility and sterility, this floor maintains the spa’s earthy palette while supporting advanced facial and skincare treatments.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.c